<L>And &s;aints around him throng,</L>
<L>The church on earth with joy &s;hall meet,</L>
<L>And join the heavenly &s;ong.</L>
</LG>
<LG>
<HEAD><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"></HEAD>
